{
  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nTranslations in languages other than en, e.g., cn, need their own directory.\r\n\r\nAnd we have doc PR #2194, a Chinese translation, waiting in the wings.\r\n\r\n## Suggestions\r\n\r\nLook at GNU, Debian, and other projects to see their practices.\r\n\r\n## UPDATE\r\n\r\nMaybe this:\r\n\r\n    doc/\r\n        en/\r\n            page404.pod6\r\n            Language/\r\n            ...duplicate current default English version under doc/\r\n        cn/\r\n        ...\r\n\r\n\r\n",
